author: Just Jared
title: Nicole Kidman & Keith Urban Share Cute Red Carpet Moment at SAG Awards 2017!
text:
Nicole Kidman and her husband Keith Urban share a super cute moment on the red carpet at the 2017 Screen Actors Guild Awards on Sunday (January 29) in Los Angeles.
The 49-year-old actress is nominated tonight for Outstanding Performance by a Female Actor in a Supporting Role for her work in the movie Lion .
FYI: Nicole is wearing a Gucci emerald sequin gown featuring multicolored feather and beaded parrot embroidered sleeves, plunging neckline and skirt with black tulle cascading ruffles. She completed her look with Stuart Weitzman heels, a Kotur clutch, an Omega watch, and Fred Leighton jewels.
